{"tid":455003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人記得超速搖搖","createTime":"2017-11-01T16:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T09:31:08.000Z","uid":62063,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f968e31e1f967a1a04b2388b4c6648cf63b7fa","tid":455003,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"漫畫同動畫都有出過，TVB亦都有播過動畫。<br />\n當年睇佢哋拎個搖搖揈嚟揈去真係好鬼型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/001741_1de547933ccdba00e57113e76597c6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F001741_1de547933ccdba00e57113e76597c6ad.jpg&h=ffbe78f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記得當年係出街見到唔少人一路行一路玩<br />\n一開始玩花老翻又卡又剩，尤其係扭蛋扭嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾經辛苦先求到屋企買個正版，日日一返到屋企就係咁對住張有勁多花式動作嘅紙練習，隻手指俾條繩勒到勁痛，印象中到最後淨係學識兩三種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/002657_f4b9a3da29ba1fd7dc41cac405e56e5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F002657_f4b9a3da29ba1fd7dc41cac405e56e5c.jpg&h=7b508282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我哋而家笑啲小學生啲手指陀螺唔知有咩好玩，但其實我哋以前都同佢哋差唔多"},{"pid":"f746f244ad3835d2cce5dd803332d3b7ec92e3aa","tid":455003,"uid":154963,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"舞動超速龍球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62eddf4fb5f9c976606f9629d271e87d5e4a4cbd","tid":455003,"uid":117821,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"我仲記得個副主角個搖搖 係夜光， 跟住我買左放左係盞燈到吸光 唔記得囉返落黎 跟住囉返黎熔撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個心好痛 我全部零用錢"},{"pid":"de6377831ba32e43be6ac5a93cc0abbff7ed574c","tid":455003,"uid":12073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy